history.content:
Exam season can be stressful! Come take a break from studying during RRR week to de-stress, decompress, and refresh, hosted by your fabulous student organizations! 
Study De-stress #1
Monday, May 4th, 2pm-7pm
Location: Wozniak Lounge
Join us for snacks, board games, or a generally chill time
Hosted by HKN
Study De-stress #2
Tuesday, May 5th, 1pm-4pm, 5pm-8pm
Location: Wozniak Lounge
Join us for snacks, board games, or a generally chill time
Hosted by HKN
Brunch in the Breezeway
Wednesday, May 6th, 11am - 1pm
Location: Breezeway between Soda hall and Etcheverry hall
Come de-stress and meet people during dead week, and enjoy bagels, coffee, orange juice, and other brunch foods in the Soda Breezeaway!
Hosted by CSUA
Tea Time + Manicures
Thursday, May 7th, 2015, 1:30pm-2:30pm
Location: 373 Soda Hall
De-stress during dead week by enjoying tea, pastries, and manicures with AWE!
Hosted by Association of Women in EECS (AWE)
history.subject: Introducing De-Stress Week!
